### Liquid Glass CSS Effect

Create a reusable `.liquid-glass` CSS class:
```css
.liquid-glass {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.01);
  background-blend-mode: luminosity;
  backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  border: none;
